Initializes a descriptor information.

Parameters:
_name - descriptor name
_type - descriptor type, e.g. no_coordinates, topological, geometrical, energegetic
_repr - descriptor representation
_docFile - base path to description file
_init - initialization class for this descriptor
_result - result class for this descriptor

Deprecated. the required dimension is strongly connected to the descriptor type, so it would be better to use the internal resolving used in #DescriptorInfo(String, String, String, String, String, String)

Initializes a descriptor information.

Parameters:
_name - descriptor name
_type - descriptor type, e.g. no_coordinates, topological, geometrical, energegetic
_dimension - descriptor coordinate dimensions: 0, 2 or 3
_repr - descriptor representation
_docFile - base path to description file
_init - initialization class for this descriptor
_result - result class for this descriptor
See Also:
TYPE_UNKNOWN, TYPE_NO_COORDINATES, TYPE_TOPOLOGICAL, TYPE_GEOMETRICAL, TYPE_ENERGETIC
